At the end of the Battle Phase, if this card attacked or was attacked: You can shuffle this card into the Deck; Special Summon 1 "Gladiator Beast" monster from your Deck, except "Gladiator Beast Lanista".

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Shuffle 2 "Gladiator Beast" cards from your hand into the Deck, then draw 3 cards.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Target 3 "Gladiator Beast" cards in your Graveyard; shuffle all 3 targets into the Deck, then draw 1 card.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Send 1 face-up "Six Samurai" monster you control to the Graveyard, then target 1 "Six Samurai" monster in either player's Graveyard; Special Summon that target.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Add 1 Level 4 or lower "Gladiator Beast" monster from your Deck to your hand.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Each time a "Six Samurai" monster(s) is Normal or Special Summoned, place 2 Bushido Counters on this card. You can remove Bushido Counters from your side of the field to activate these effects. // * 2 Counters: Target 1 face-up "Six Samurai" or "Shien" Effect Monster; that target gains 500 ATK until the End Phase. // * 4 Counters: Add 1 "Six Samurai" monster from your Deck or Graveyard to your hand. // * 6 Counters: Target 1 "Shien" Effect Monster in your Graveyard; Special Summon that target.

extendedData.value: Target 2 "Six Samurai" monsters in your Graveyard; Special Summon those targets in face-up Attack Position, then destroy them during the End Phase and take damage equal to monsters' ATK.
